LanguageData.MSE_BionicClavicleModule.label: bionic clavicle module
LanguageData.MSE_BionicClavicleModule.description: An advanced artificial clavicle module. With lattice-dust healing system allows it to recover from damage. You can install it to clavicle module slot. Requires modules surgery research to install it.
LanguageData.MSE_BionicArmModule.label: bionic arm module
LanguageData.MSE_BionicArmModule.description: An advanced artificial arm module. With its biogel nerve-link and lattice-dust healing system, it is better than a biological arm in almost every way. You can install it to arm module slot. Requires modules surgery research to install it.
